                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6859" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0072</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12669 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一体两翼：比亚迪新能源汽车的腾飞之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“One-Body-Two-Wing”Strategy: BYD&#39;s New Energy Vehicle Taking-off </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李克克，姚良雪，梁均杨，王莹，刘瀚，杜丽虹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新能源汽车；一体两翼；插电式混动；纯电动</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Energy Vehicle; One-Body-Two-Wing; Plug in Hybrid Vehicle; Blade Electric Vehicle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021年，比亚迪新能源汽车迎来市场大爆发，多款车型的持续热销使其荣登行业销冠，比亚迪真正实现腾飞。凭借多年的自主研发和产业链布局，比亚迪在垂直整合和技术创新上形成强大优势，为其在新能源汽车领域的发展奠定坚实基础。在刀片电池、DM-i超级混动技术以及e3.0平台的助力下，比亚迪在提供平稳过渡方案的插混领域和被视为未来技术主流的纯电动方向分别站稳脚跟，“插混+纯电”的“一体两翼”战略布局逐渐形成，成为其驰骋新能源汽车市场的制胜法宝。随着智能化汽车新赛道的帷幕徐徐拉开，作为自主品牌的佼佼者，比亚迪也将面临新的机遇和挑战。本案例聚焦比亚迪“插混+纯电”的“一体两翼”战略布局，结合2021年以来新能源汽车行业的最新演变，解析了比亚迪在行业普遍遇冷之下，实现逆势增长的销量密码。比亚迪的一系列实践对其他传统汽车企业的转型和决策制定具有重要借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sales of BYD&#39;s new energy vehicle have seen explosive growth in 2021, which has made BYD the top seller in the industry. With many years of independent R&amp;D and industrial chain layout, BYD has shaped competitive advantages of vertical integration and technological innovation, which has laid a solid foundation for its leading role of new energy vehicle industry. Armed with blade battery, DM-i super hybrid technology and platform e3.0, BYD has gained its foothold in fields of both Plug in Hybrid Vehicle (PHV), a transition auto product, and the Blade Electric Vehicle (BEV), a potential dominant product of the future. The business structure of “PHV plus BEV”, described as “One-Body-Two-Wing” strategy, has gradually formed and become a trump card for BYD to win the market. With the autonomous vehicle market is emerging, BYD, as one of the best national brands will be facing new changes and opportunities. This case focuses on BYD&#39;s “One-Body-Two-Wing” strategy and explores the secret of BYD&#39;s sales success amid the current trends of auto industry since 2021. It has significant implications for the transformation and decision-making of other traditional automobile enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">需求变动影响因素；供给变动影响因素；应用需求和供给分析行业变化市场界定；市场结构的划分和类型；市场集中度测算市场势力的定义；市场势力的来源；获取市场势力的方法产业链垂直整合；规模经济；范围经济；交易成本；网络效应智能汽车的特点和盈利模式；企业智能化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
